I would think that they'd obviously ask me what preference of meat I'd wanted, and I would've glady told them, if they didn't already know. The average person that orders that would want grilled chicken!🤷🏽 In addition, I paid $62 for all 3 nasty alfredo's. LASTLY, I noticed dead roaches in the box, which is key to this whole thing! This place is atrocious and overly pricey for such under average food. AVOID!!
